%html
  %head
    %title="OC HomeMasters, You've Downgraded Your Listing"
  %body
    %p 
      = "#{@user.listing.company_name},"
    %p
      This email is to notify you that your premium listing on OC HomeMasters has been downgraded to a free listing.
    %p
      You can always upgrade to premium by visiting this url:
      %br
      = link_to new_upgrade_url, new_upgrade_url
    %p
      You can manage your listing by logging in to your account here:
      %br
      = link_to new_user_session_url, new_user_session_url
    %p
      Sincerely,
    %p
      The OC HomeMasters Team
      %br
      = link_to root_url, root_url